"title": "3030: Holy Spirit, power of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3030: holy spirit, power of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit equips and empowers believers so that the reign and reality of God is revealed through them in the world.</p>\n<h2>The power of the Holy Spirit is witnessed to in the OT</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2-Isa11:3\">ISA 11:2–11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit will show his power on the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:15\">ISA 32:15</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The Spirit's power will enable people to serve God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26-Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:26–36:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a></p>\n<h3>The Spirit's power will prompt prophecy and visions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17-Acts2:18\">ACT 2:17–2:18</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power is described by OT imagery</h2>\n<p>Oil:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:1\">1SA 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:11-Isa63:12\">ISA 63:11–63:12</a> <em>the arm of God</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:14\">EZK 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1\">EZK 37:1</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power is demonstrated in the OT</h2>\n<h3>In creation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a></p>\n<h3>In acts of judgment and war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">JDG 6:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">JDG 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:6\">1SA 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>In the lives of his servants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:17\">NUM 11:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power is seen in the life of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>In his conception</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a></strong></p>\n<h3>In his teaching and ministry</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:28-Matt7:29\">MAT 7:28–7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28\">MAT 12:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:22\">MRK 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:27\">MRK 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">LUK 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17\">LUK 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h3>In his resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:16\">1TI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power is seen in the church's mission</h2>\n<h3>In the church's witness and preaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:7\">ACT 16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4\">1CO 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>In the apostolic ministry of signs and wonders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>In miraculous works in the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">1CO 12:28</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power builds Christian character</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7\">2TI 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's power strengthens the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:11\">ROM 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:7-1Cor1:8\">1CO 1:7–1:8</a></p>",
